LOCATION: MULLINS PARK CORAL SPRINGS 10000 NW 29TH ST CORAL SPRINGS FL, 33065 NO AUTOGRAPHS, VIDEOGRAPHY (VIDEOS). SOCIAL MEDIA LIVES, OR PHOTOS ARE ALLOWED. node.text:
#Truzz We are back again! Bring ALL the KIDZ!!! Thiz iz a FREE EVENT! Register on the link provided! NO AUTOGRAPHS/ PICTURES ON EITHER DAY! 
Lamar desires to enjoy the children and festivities respectively.  Ages 4&up #sponsored by Era8apparel (IF YOU DO NOT REGISTER YOUR CHILDREN ONLINE THEY WILL NOT BE ABLE TO PARTICIPATE NO EXCEPTIONS) 

Saturday Only: 

Water slides 
Obstacles Course 
Train Ride 
Go Karts 
Game Truck 
3 Legged Race 
Sack Race 
Relay Run 
DJ 
Food Vendors 

Sunday: 

7vs7  tournament 
Food Vendors 
DJ 
Copy and paste the link below 👇🏾 to register  if you can’t please go to www.eventbrite.com
https://www.eventbrite.com/e/fun-day-with-lj-tickets-156279140115
